{"tid":797104,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"估地方？少婦外送遭下藥性家人發現當冇事 射足17次後才將惡狼遭收押","createTime":"2018-08-28T09:03:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-28T09:22:46.000Z","uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a320b09cb5f6ef71a63d4d07ed687ed79cd61f0e","tid":797104,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T09:03:15.000Z","msg":"彰化傅姓男子(37歲)覬覦一間餐廳少婦美色，常叫外送和少婦聊天，也會請少婦喝飲料，未料今年一月間傅男竟在飲料下藥，再伺機性侵，半年多來還用影片恐嚇少婦，前後性侵17次，還威脅少婦一起吸食安非他命，少婦本月上旬受不了報案，檢方昨清晨搜索傅男家查扣性愛影片，檢方聲押傅男，今天下午法院裁准羈押。<br />\n<br />\n被害人家中經營餐廳，婚後仍在娘家幫忙，有時幫忙外送，傅男覬覦少婦美色，常藉口叫外送，實則要與少婦聊天，放長線釣大魚，並趁外送的時候請喝飲料「慰勞辛苦」，少婦因對方是熟客也不疑有他，逐漸失去戒心。<br />\n今年一月間，少婦外送後又喝了傅男的飲料卻昏迷遭性侵，少婦家人疑惑超過外送時間太久，前往查看，但窗縫中只見傅男壓著少婦，但雙方衣著完整，不過少婦回家後，一度頭暈跌倒，懷疑遭下藥，但當時並未報案。<br />\n過沒多久，傅男即連絡少婦，並以手中握有兩人性愛影片及少婦裸照為由，要求做愛，少婦不堪恐嚇，半年多來再被性侵16次。彰化地檢署檢察官蔡勝浩獲報後蒐集相關證據，聲請搜索票，昨拂曉指揮彰化縣警局婦幼隊搜索。<br />\n檢方查扣傅男用來拍攝性愛影片及裸照的平板和手機各一台，內有被害人被性侵及猥褻的影像，影片中還有傅男強逼少婦吸食安非他命，但被害人極力抵抗，因此未得逞。<br />\n檢方訊問後認為傅男所涉加重性交罪重大，且有反覆實施之虞，向法院聲押，由於深夜未偵訊，上午11點聲押庭開到下午1點多，法院裁准羈押傅男。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20180828/1419471\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20180828%2F1419471&d=yWPJG85ZHa9pNZf8Pcydo10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=debaed08\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20180828%2F1419471&h=9909aaf4\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20180828/1419471</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 賺了16次"},{"pid":"7dd2d56fd665b01d629c94f253720719741946ae","tid":797104,"uid":53553,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T09:03:54.000Z","msg":"睇字都扯左"},{"pid":"294eddeb71a24526ef1ca635fc7e52d9a67cb6a6","tid":797104,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7dd2d56fd665b01d629c94f253720719741946ae","tid":797104,"uid":53553,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T09:03:54.000Z","msg":"睇字都扯左"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T09:05:40.000Z","msg":"清醒有16次，一定有迫佢一路做一路打埋老公"},{"pid":"dc78230c287cbc803f119cb58df54d3ec14d69e7","tid":797104,"uid":144035,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T09:05:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c256eaaaaf13601ea3132dbc17f4fa760fe55355","tid":797104,"uid":9286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T09:07:10.000Z","msg":"藏毒 有排坐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c9f691cdbbfe0b1206b4a9e85e0a5182ecf8cf6","tid":797104,"uid":13867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"294eddeb71a24526ef1ca635fc7e52d9a67cb6a6","tid":797104,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7dd2d56fd665b01d629c94f253720719741946ae","tid":797104,"uid":53553,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T09:03:54.000Z","msg":"睇字都扯左"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T09:05:40.000Z","msg":"清醒有16次，一定有迫佢一路做一路打埋老公"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T09:09:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af841d1488b839873633ca65c2d58ac12141b604","tid":797104,"uid":72009,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T09:10:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://article.cfd888.info/file/n14344/0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Farticle.cfd888.info%2Ffile%2Fn14344%2F0.jpg&h=588bc017&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n感覺上似依Ｄ"},{"pid":"e412dceffdf1a93d457fc1075dc83683c996a36a","tid":797104,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"af841d1488b839873633ca65c2d58ac12141b604","tid":797104,"uid":72009,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T09:10:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://article.cfd888.info/file/n14344/0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Farticle.cfd888.info%2Ffile%2Fn143